{"tid":95273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中資又搶地","createTime":"2017-01-26T01:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T10:39:57.000Z","uid":27534,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f003b8cdf7b32be483467ad69e5bb713297a683","tid":95273,"uid":27534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:43:12.000Z","msg":"\\\\海航集團系內公司昨再下一城，以逾 55.29 億元奪啟德第 1L 區 1 號地盤住宅地，平均樓面呎價高達 1.3 萬元<br />\n<br />\n是次地皮成交價逾 55.29 億元，樓面呎價高達 1.3 萬元，不但較市場估計最高 1.2 萬元大幅高出約 8.3%，相比香港發展商嘉華國際（00173）上月奪得的第 1K 區 2 號地盤樓面呎價 10,220 元，是次呎價相隔不足一個月高出多達 27.2%。<br />\n<br />\n3 幅地皮共斥資 197 億<br />\n<br />\n事實上，海航系內連環癲價搶啟德地皮，並且獨攬三幅啟德呎價最高地皮，成為該區勢力範圍最大發展商，其中海航實業國際於去年十一月及十二月，分別以逾 88.37 億元及逾 54.12 億元投得啟德第 1K 區 3 號地盤及 1L 區 3 號地盤兩幅住宅地，樓面呎價 1.35 萬元及 1.36 萬元，連環創九龍東呎價最高地皮新高紀錄。\\\\<br />\n<br />\n又以本傷人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個啟德都係中資樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n起好咪要2萬幾蚊呎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc269f7248d2e9c84c89cc2088c2f7efe255e46","tid":95273,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:44:34.000Z","msg":"中國日日印錢怕咩？"},{"pid":"50e5ae66510554d757905b77e0038048e5a7963f","tid":95273,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:52:47.000Z","msg":"走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b142c5554fca6522bce0acfa21b5db6ac12a48a2","tid":95273,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:06:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />